## 1. Definitions
"Software" means the source code, documentation, and all associated files provided under this License.
"Licensee" means any natural or legal person using the Software.
"Modification" means any alteration, enhancement, or adaptation of the Software.
"Distribution" means any form of sharing, publication, or making available of the Software.
"Principal Project" means the official repository maintained by NEHONIX.
"Commercial Use" means use of the Software in a commercial, marketing, or promotional context.

## 2. Grant of Rights
Subject to strict compliance with all conditions of this License, NEHONIX grants the Licensee the following rights:

### 2.1 Use
- Use of the Software for personal, educational, or commercial purposes.
- Execution of the Software on any compatible system.

### 2.2 Modification
- Modification of the Software to adapt it to specific needs.
